manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Optimal Storage with Style and Function Bring harmony to your bath or shower space with a wide variety of storage and accessory items from mDesign. Keep toiletries tucked into their designated spots with our extensive lines of shower caddies, beauty organizers, vanity or countertop shelves and canisters. Keep towels neatly rolled or folded with a wall mounted holder rack. Add a pop of color to your decor with a festive bathmat, rug, or shower curtain. mDesign carries endless options that optimize your master or guest bathroom and make you feel like you’re relaxing at a regal spa getaway.

Add a Pop of Color with a Decorative Waterproof Polyester Printed Shower Curtain with Reinforced Buttonholes Shower curtains are a great and hassle-free way to add a statement to your bathroom. mDesign’s printed shower curtains come in an array of colors, patterns, and lengths to fit any size shower. The exceptional polyester fabric promotes water beading and is smooth to resist moisture-rich bath and shower environments. Reinforced buttonholes are great for any type of rings or hooks.

Storage Canisters, Baskets, Trays, and Holders Maximize Cabinet, Countertop, or Vanity Space Modern and Minimal Dispensers for Foaming, Liquid, or Bar Soaps Available in an array of sizes, styles, colors, and finishes, mDesign offers soap dispensers, canisters, and dishes that bring an elegant flourish to your bathroom. These versatile holders are perfect for foaming, liquid, or bar soaps. Decorative Freestanding Toilet Tissue Holders, Stands, and Baskets If your aesthetic is modern, traditional, elegant, or casual, mDesign offers your choice of woven baskets, over-the-tank wall mounts, metal rust-resistant towers, or plastic holders that conveniently fit next to your toilet or sink. Each piece features an easy-access opening to hold extra rolls of toilet paper. Choose a multi-purpose rack for magazines, towelettes, sponges, or extra soap. Organize Shampoo, Conditioner, and Body Wash with Free-Standing and Hanging Shower Caddies Keep shampoos, conditioners, body scrubs, washcloths, razors, and loofas neat and tidy with mDesign’s essential shower caddies. These caddies come in your choice of metal or plastic and fit in cozy corners, around showerheads, or over doors for maximum storage space. Our caddies provide drainage that prevent mold and mildew. Grab a portable caddy with handles for on-the-go use in a college dorm. Durable Trash Cans for Cabinets, Under Counters, Next to Sinks, and Other Small Nooks Wastebaskets from mDesign keep garbage out of sight and add style to any room. Offered in metal or plastic with or without a lid, multiple colors, and different shapes and sizes, these bins hold trash and can be tucked away or stored in plain sight.

Cosmetic Beauty Organizers Keep Makeup and Beauty Essentials Sorted in One Place Makeup, brushes, accessories, cleansers, lotions, nail polish, and even jewelry have their own designated spot with mDesign’s cosmetic trays, wire baskets, caddies, or organizers with drawers. Minimize bathroom clutter by keeping all your beauty essentials in one place. Create a customized area on countertops, vanities, in cabinets, inside drawers, or tucked beneath the sink with these compartmentalized holders.

mDesign - Solutions for Home. Solutions for Life. Whether you’re organizing your bathroom, living room, bedroom, office, playroom, or laundry room, mDesign has you covered. Our wide variety of products are stylish, purposeful, and affordable. De-clutter your home with confidence when you shop with mDesign.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love these and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: These are great. You can chose any color and it would look good. Holds a ton and not gaudy. Have one on the small bathroom and two is the double vanity on each side. Love them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bathroom sink clutter beater!
reviews.reviewText: Perfect perfect perfect! My bathroom sink counter looks so much more efficient with vertical surfaces to use. The corner shape makes the whole space on each level accessible for frequent use, so no losing things in a hard-to-reach void.Setting it up was the easiest thing in the world, the legs pop out like they WANT to be in the steady position.Another benefit of the triangle shape - incredibly stable with no wobble, even if the legs might sit a little unevenly in grout lines on my ceramic tiled bathroom counter.I've been on an organizing and de-clutter kick, and this is one of my favorite purchases because its usefulness is more than worth its reasonable price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I was looking for
reviews.reviewText: Great shelf! I searched Amazon for the perfect corner shelf for all my little stuff. The clutter was making me crazy! They came timely, don’t require any tools (the legs just fold down), plenty of room underneath, little grooves to hold the legs if I had decided to stack them, and great price. I’m very happy with the bronze color. Looks good in my bathroom.
